h3. Credentials Storage

{info}
All credentials are stored securely in AWS Secrets Manager. *Never hardcode passwords in documentation or scripts.*

*Secret Location:*
* *Secret Name:* {{org-infrastructure/credentials}}
* *Region:* {{us-east-2}}

*To retrieve:*
{code:language=bash}
aws secretsmanager get-secret-value \
  --region us-east-2 \
  --secret-id org-infrastructure/credentials \
  --query SecretString --output text | jq .
{code}

*Available Keys in Secret:*
* {{administrator_password}} - Domain admin password
* {{<username>_password}} - Individual user passwords (if stored)
{info}

